{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"id787a5255-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s698e"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"698e"},"text":"§ 698e.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Authorization of appropriations for Big Thicket Preserve","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"There are authorized to be appropriated such sums as may be necessary to carry out the provisions of sections 698 to 698e of this title, but not to exceed $63,812,000 for the acquisition of lands and interests in lands and not to exceed $7,000,000 for development. Effective ","children":[{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1984-10-01"},"text":"October 1, 1984","children":[],"tail":", there is authorized to be appropriated such sums as may be necessary for the acquisition of the visitor contact and administrative site referred to in subsection (c) of "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t16/s698"},"text":"section 698 of this title","children":[],"tail":". Effective upon "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1993-07-01"},"text":"July 1, 1993","children":[],"tail":", there is authorized to be appropriated such sums as may be necessary to carry out the purposes of subsections (c) and (d) of "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t16/s698"},"text":"section 698 of this title","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"id787a5256-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/93/439/s6"},"text":"Pub. L. 93–439, § 6","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1974-10-11"},"text":"Oct. 11, 1974","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/88/1257"},"text":"88 Stat. 1257","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/98/489/s1/b"},"text":"Pub. L. 98–489, § 1(b)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"